/li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"november2013\">23 November 2013</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>[TASK] Update all extensions to latest</li>\r\n<li>[TASK] Update Twitter Bootstrap 3.0.2</li>\r\n<li>[TASK] Re-organize files within Storage. Add public / private storage</li>\r\n<li>[BUGFIX] Anchor next to h1 title didnâ€™t show up anymore</li>\r\n<li>[RELEASE] Version <a href=\"https://github.com/Ecodev/bootstrap_package/releases/tag/1.3.0\">1.3.0</a> - complete <a href=\"https://github.com/Ecodev/bootstrap_package/compare/1.2.2...1.3.0\">change log</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"october2013\">31 October 2013</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Update all extensions to latest</li>\r\n<li>Update Twitter Bootstrap 3.0.1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"august2013\">16 August 2013</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Update <a href=\"http://wiki.typo3.org/TYPO3_6.1.5\">TYPO3 6.1.5</a></li>\r\n<li>Update all extensions to latest</li>\r\n<li>Update Twitter Bootstrap 3.0</li>\r\n<li>Remove clear cache language menu in the BE which has become obsolete</li>\r\n<li>Remove the list page which was not working</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"august2013\">08 August 2013</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Configure default scheduler tasks</li>\r\n<li>Better styling of indexed search pagination</li>\r\n<li>Remove CSS concatenation preventing cache clearing annoyance</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"august2013\">02 August 2013</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Release version <a href=\"https://github.com/Ecodev/bootstrap_package/releases/tag/1.2.2\">1.2.2</a></li>\r\n<li>Update <a href=\"http://wiki.typo3.org/TYPO3_6.1.3\">TYPO3 6.1.3</a></li>\r\n<li>Update all extensions to latest</li>\r\n<li>Fix a few glitches thanks to <a href=\"https://github.com/oliversalzburg\">oliversalzburg</a>. Check out complete change log.</li>\r\n<li>Complete <a href=\"https://github.com/Ecodev/bootstrap_package/compare/1.2.1...1.2.2\">change log</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"july2013\">25 July 2013</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Release version <a href=\"https://github.com/Ecodev/bootstrap_package/releases/tag/1.2.1\">1.2.1</a></li>\r\n<li>Update <a href=\"http://wiki.typo3.org/TYPO3_6.1.2\">TYPO3 6.1.2</a></li>\r\n<li>Update all extensions to latest</li>\r\n<li>Activate indexing of pages and configure <a href=\"/index.php?id=17\">search plugin</a></li>\r\n<li>Complete <a href=\"https://github.com/Ecodev/bootstrap_package/compare/1.1.1...1.2.1\">change log</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"july2013\">22 July 2013</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Release version <a href=\"https://github.com/Ecodev/bootstrap_package/releases/tag/1.1.1\">1.1.1</a></li>\r\n<li>Improve English texts thanks to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/tony_lush\">Tony Lush</a></li>\r\n<li>Update all Fedext extensions with master version including <a href=\"http://fedext.net/news/flux-forms-revisited.html\">Flux Forms Revisited</a></li>\r\n<li>Complete <a href=\"https://github.com/Ecodev/bootstrap_package/compare/1.1.0...1.1.1\">change log</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"july2013\">17 July 2013</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Release version <a href=\"https://github.com/Ecodev/bootstrap_package/releases/tag/1.1.0\">1.1.0</a></li>\r\n<li>Clean up migrated files across the website</li>\r\n<li>Add <a href=\"/index.php?id=94\">new page</a> with extension infinite scroll gallery to illustrate Media possibilities</li>\r\n<li>Add German translation (thanks to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ntzwbr\">Andreas Neumann</a>)</li>\r\n<li>Update all extensions with master version</li>\r\n<li>Fix github #<a href=\"https://github.com/Ecodev/bootstrap_package/issues/16\">16</a>, #<a href=\"https://github.com/Ecodev/bootstrap_package/issues/17\">17</a>, #<a href=\"https://github.com/Ecodev/bootstrap_package/issues/19\">19</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"june2013\">14 June 2013</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Update all extensions to current master (except EXT:vhs which is unstable for now).</li>\r\n<li>Add extension nc_staticfilecache for static file caching.</li>\r\n<li>Add page about performance &#8220;